{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTE2MTI5MDY0", "number": 776, "title": "Add method to enable/disable periodic flush on send in the EventProducer", "bodyText": "BMM has a flushless mode, where the connector keeps track of all acknowledged sends for every TopicPartition and commits offsets based on these. The EventProducer tries to flush periodically on send, and this lands up calling flush even in flushless mode. This PR adds the capability to configure the EventProducer as flushless.\nImportant: DO NOT REPORT SECURITY ISSUES DIRECTLY ON GITHUB.\nFor reporting security issues and contributing security fixes,\nplease, email security@linkedin.com instead, as described in\nthe contribution guidelines.\nPlease, take a minute to review the contribution guidelines at:\nhttps://github.com/linkedin/Brooklin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md", "createdAt": "2020-11-05T15:07:41Z", "url": "https://github.com/linkedin/brooklin/pull/776", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "cad06601d1c82c18843f656f569d9ac81690274b"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-11-10T19:21:05Z", "author": {"login": "somandal"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 9, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdZjwSrAH2gAyNTE2MTI5MDY0OjY5YjVmNmFlYWQ2Mjk3ZjBkOGQzMWIyZDIyODg2NDgyOTE2Yzg4MWY=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdbOB1gAFqTUyNzUxMjcxNw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "69b5f6aead6297f0d8d31b2d22886482916c881f", "author": {"user": {"login": "somandal", "name": "Sonam Mandal"}}, "url": "https://github.com/linkedin/brooklin/commit/69b5f6aead6297f0d8d31b2d22886482916c881f", "committedDate": "2020-11-05T15:04:46Z", "message": "Add flushless config to EventProducer to allow disabling periodic flush on send"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTI0NTMwNTg3", "url": "https://github.com/linkedin/brooklin/pull/776#pullrequestreview-524530587", "created